ve%20Take%20On%20Rohit's%20IPL%20Future%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EStar%20India%20off-spinner%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20shared%20his%20views%20saying%20that%20opener%20Rohit%20Sharma%20will%20not%20leave%20the%20Mumbai%20Indians%20franchise%20and%20will%20continue%20playing%20for%20the%20franchise%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202025%20season.%20Last%20year%2C%20Hardik%20replaced%20Rohit%20as%20the%20skipper%20of%20one%20of%20the%20most%20successful%20franchises%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20tournament.%20The%20decision%20from%20the%20franchise%20didn't%20go%20down%20well%20with%20some%20sections%20of%20the%20fanbase%20which%20led%20to%20some%20criticism.%20%26quot%3BEven%20if%20you%20think%20like%20Rohit%2C%20it's%20not%20wrong%20at%20all.%20I%20don't%20want%20any%20headache.%20I%20have%20been%20a%20captain%20for%20India.%20I%20have%20captained%20Mumbai%20many%20times.%20Even%20if%20I%20am%20not%20a%20captain%2C%20I%20am%20going%20to%20Mumbai%20happily.%20If%20I%20play%20for%20Mumbai%2C%20it's%20super.%20I%20am%20sure%20most%20players%20are%20like%20that.%20After%20a%20stage%2C%20money%20doesn't%20matter%20for%20some%20of%20those%20players.%20That's%20the%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20said%20on%20his%20YouTube%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20had%20a%20decent%20IPL%202024%20season%20with%20the%20bat%2C%20scoring%20417%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2032.07%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20150.%20He%20scored%20a%20century%20and%20fifty%2C%20with%20the%20best%20score%20of%20105*.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20has%20been%20an%20absolute%20legend%20for%20the%20Mumbai%20Indians.%20Since%20joining%20the%20franchise%20as%20a%20bright%20up-and-coming%20talent%20back%20in%202011%2C%20Rohit%20has%20played%20199%20IPL%20matches%20in%20Blue%20and%20Gold%20clothing%2C%20scoring%205%2C084%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2029.39%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20129.86.%20He%20has%20scored%20a%20century%20and%2034%20fifties%20in%20195%20innings%20for%20MI%2C%20with%20the%20best%20score%20of%20109*.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20taking%20over%20the%20captaincy%20of%20the%20franchise%20from%20Ricky%20Ponting%20in%202013%2C%20Rohit%20took%20MI%20to%20their%20golden%20period%2C%20winning%20the%20trophy%20five%20times%20in%2010%20years%20(2013%2C%202015%2C%202017%2C%202019%20and%202020)%20and%20reaching%20playoffs%20twice.%20Hardik%20Pandya%20replaced%20him%20as%20the%20captain%20last%20year%20after%20making%20a%20move%20to%20the%20franchise%20that%20made%20him%20a%20star%20following%20two%20great%20years%20with%20the%20Gujarat%20Titans%20(GT)%2C%20including%20the%20title-winning%20debut%20season%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20has%20also%20won%20two%20Champions%20League%20T20%20titles%20with%20MI%20in%202011%20and%202013%2C%20the%20latter%20as%20a%20captain.%20The%20'Hitman'%20is%20MI's%20all-time%20highest%20run-getter%2C%20scoring%205%2C357%20runs%20in%20208%20matches%20and%20204%20innings%20at%20an%20average%20of%2029.59%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20almost%20130%2C%20with%20a%20century%20and%2035%20fifties%20in%20204%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20youngster%2C%20Rohit%20also%20represented%20the%20now-defunct%20Deccan%20Chargers%2C%20a%20former%20Hyderabad%20franchise%20from%202008-2010.%20He%20played%2045%20matches%20for%20the%20team%2C%20scoring%201%2C170%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2030.79%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20over%20131%2C%20with%20eight%20fifties%20in%2044%20innings.%20His%20best%20score%20was%2076*.%20He%20won%20the%20IPL%202009%20season%20with%20this%20franchise%2C%20making%20him%20a%20six-time%20IPL%20champion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20veteran%20batter%20is%20the%20fourth-highest%20run-getter%20in%20IPL%20history%2C%20scoring%206%2C254%20runs%20in%20244%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2029.63%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20130.15.%20He%20scored%20a%20century%20and%2042%20fifties%20in%20239%20innings%2C%20with%20the%20best%20score%20of%20109*.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725021600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fb4di88fg_rohit-sharma-mi-bcci_625x300_26_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fmoney-doesnt-matter-ravichandran-ashwins-massive-take-on-rohit-sharmas-ipl-future-6441767%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20shared%20his%20views%20saying%20that%20opener%20Rohit%20Sharma%20will%20not%20leave%20the%20Mumbai%20Indians%20franchise%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202025%20season.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%202-Hour%20Namaz%20Break%20In%20Assam%20Assembly%20On%20Fridays%20For%20Muslim%20MLAs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Assam%20assembly%20has%20decided%20to%20scrap%20its%20decades-old%20rule%20of%20giving%20a%20two-hour%20namaz%20break%20for%20Muslim%20legislators%20on%20Fridays.%20The%20assembly%20rules%20committee%20today%20adopted%20a%20resolution%20today%20to%20continue%20the%20business%20of%20the%20House%20on%20Friday%20like%20other%20days.%20Till%20today%2C%20the%20Assam%20assembly%20used%20to%20adjourn%20for%20two%20hours%20on%20Fridays%20to%20allow%20the%20Muslim%20MLAs%20to%20attend%20the%20namaz%20prayers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20Assam%20Legislative%20Assembly%2C%20the%20sitting%20of%20the%20Assembly%20on%20Friday%20used%20to%20be%20adjourned%20at%2011%20am%20to%20facilitate%20Muslim%20members%20to%20go%20for%20namaz.%20The%20assembly%20used%20to%20resume%20its%20proceedings%20in%20the%20post-lunch%20session%20after%20the%20Muslim%20members%20came%20back%20from%20the%20namaz.%20On%20all%20other%20days%2C%20the%20House%20used%20to%20conduct%20its%20proceedings%20without%20any%20such%20adjournment%20for%20religious%20purposes%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20press%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BShri%20Biswajit%20Daimary%2C%20Hon'ble%20Speaker%20took%20note%20of%20this%20matter%20and%20in%20view%20of%20the%20secular%20nature%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20proposed%20that%20the%20Assam%20Legislative%20Assembly%20must%20conduct%20its%20proceedings%20on%20Fridays%20like%20any%20other%20day%20without%20any%20adjournment%20to%20facilitate%20Muslim%20members%20to%20go%20for%20namaz%2C%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20doing%20away%20with%20the%202-hour%20Jumma%20break%2C%20%40AssamAssembly%20has%20prioritised%20productivity%20and%20shed%20another%20vestige%20of%20colonial%20baggage.%20This%20practice%20was%20introduced%20by%20Muslim%20League's%20Syed%20Saadulla%20in%201937%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EBy%20doing%20away%20with%20the%202%20hour%20Jumma%20break%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAssamAssembly%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40AssamAssembly%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20prioritised%20productivity%20and%20shed%20another%20vestige%20of%20colonial%20baggage.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThis%20practice%20was%20introduced%20by%20Muslim%20League's%20Syed%20Saadulla%20in%201937.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMy%20gratitude%20to%20Hon'ble%20Speaker%20Shri%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBiswajitDaimar5%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40BiswajitDaimar5%3C%2Fa%3E%20dangoriya%20and%20our%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20(%40himantabiswa)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhimantabiswa%2Fstatus%2F1829443011656167666%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2030%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20has%20criticised%20the%20move%20and%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Bhurts%20Muslim%20sentiments%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Fridays%2C%20there%20will%20be%20trouble%20in%20those%20two%20hours%20if%20any%20important%20bill%20comes%20for%20discussion%2C%20we%20might%20not%20be%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20AIUDF%20MLA%20Rafikul%20Islam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20party%20colleague%20Mujibur%20Rehman%20alleged%2C%20%26quot%3BSo%20many%20chief%20ministers%20came%20but%20no%20one%20tried%20this%20but%20Himanta%20Biswas%20Sarma%20is%20only%20doing%20this%20to%20hurt%20the%20Muslim%20sentiments%20and%20create%20a%20divide%20between%20and%20Hindus%20Muslims%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20MLA%20Jakir%20Hussain%20Sikdar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20has%20been%20a%20tradition%20and%20a%20trend%20that%20the%20House%20followed%20for%20decades.%20They%20decided%20to%20change%20it%20but%20was%20there%20a%20broader%20consultation%3F%20They%20have%20to%20explain%20why%20this%20decision%20was%20taken.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20MLA%20Taranga%20Gogoi%20welcomed%20the%20move%20and%20said%20there%20should%20not%20be%20special%20rules%20for%20one%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20secular%20country%20and%20inside%20the%20assembly%2C%20there%20should%20not%20be%20special%20rules%20for%20one%20community%20so%20we%20welcome%20this%20decision.%20If%20they%20need%20to%20offer%20namaz%20they%20can%20have%20a%20separate%20room%20like%20in%20airports%20etc.%20They%20cannot%20have%20separate%20arrangements.%20Every%20Friday%2C%20the%20House%20used%20to%20be%20adjourned%20for%20two%20hours.%20This%20was%20a%20waste%20of%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20resolution%2C%20Assam%20is%20set%20to%20another%20pre-Independence%20era%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20the%20assembly%20passed%20a%20Bill%20that%20would%20require%20compulsory%20registration%20of%20Muslim%20marriages%20and%20divorces%20with%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Assembly%20passed%20the%20Assam%20Compulsory%20Registration%20of%20Muslim%20Marriages%20and%20Divorces%20Bill%2C%202024%2C%20aiming%20to%20safeguard%20the