%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Now%20That%20Champai%20Soren%20Is%20Finally%20With%20BJP%2C%20Can%20He%20Help%20It%20Win%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Flkhaoh28_champai_625x300_30_August_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Jharkhand%2C%20Champai%20Soren%20of%20the%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20(JMM)%2C%20joined%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20today%2C%20ending%20days%20of%20speculation.%20'Tiger'%2C%20as%20Soren%20is%20fondly%20called%2C%20is%20a%20strong%20tribal%20leader%20with%20a%20credible%20image.%20He%20is%20considered%20the%20right-hand%20man%20of%20JMM%20patriarch%20Shibu%20Soren%20and%20played%20a%20big%20role%20in%20the%20movement%20to%20carve%20out%20a%20separate%20state%20of%20Jharkhand%20from%20Bihar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Soren's%20entry%2C%20the%20BJP%20hopes%20to%20make%20a%20dent%20in%20the%20ST%20vote%20bank%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20comprising%20the%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20(JMM)%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD).%20It%20also%20boosts%20the%20BJP's%20chances%20of%20making%20a%20comeback%20in%20the%20state%20by%20exploiting%20the%20anti-incumbency%20against%20the%20Hemant%20Soren%20government%20amidst%20allegations%20of%20unfulfilled%20promises.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP's%20Need%20For%20A%20Stalwart%20Leader%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChampai%20was%20appointed%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20after%20Hemant%20Soren%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20in%20February%202024.%20Under%20his%20leadership%2C%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20won%20five%20of%20the%2014%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state%2C%20three%20more%20than%20the%20last%20time.%20The%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20won%20all%20the%20five%20ST-reserved%20seats%20in%20the%20state%2C%20highlighting%20the%20anger%20in%20the%20community%20over%20the%20arrest%20of%20its%20leader.%20While%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20bagged%2037%25%20votes%20-%20a%20rise%20of%205%20percentage%20points%20-%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20registered%20a%20vote%20share%20of%2048%25%2C%20a%20drop%20of%208%20percentage%20points%20over%20the%20previous%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20BJP's%20losses%2C%20questions%20had%20been%20raised%20about%20the%20leadership%20of%20party%20president%20Babulal%20Marandi%20former%20chief%20minister%20and%20Arjun%20Munda.%20In%20that%20context%2C%20the%20entry%20of%20Champai%20Soren%20fulfils%20to%20some%20extent%20the%20BJP's%20need%20for%20stalwart%20tribal%20leaders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Champai%20Left%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20abrupt%20manner%20in%20which%20Champai%20Soren%20was%20asked%20to%20vacate%20the%20top%20post%20after%20the%20release%20of%20Hemant%20Soren%20hurt%20the%20'Tiger'.%20The%20JMM%20was%20born%20out%20of%20a%20struggle%20for%20a%20separate%20state.%20But%2C%20over%20the%20years%2C%20like%20any%20other%20regional%20party%2C%20%C2%A0it%20has%20become%20a%20family-controlled%20unit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20STs%20account%20for%2026.2%25%20of%20the%20state's%20population%20and%20hold%20the%20key%20to%20government%20formation.%20There%20are%2028%20ST-reserved%20seats%2C%20sixteen%20of%20which%20are%20located%20in%20the%20Santhal%20Pargana%20(northeast)%20and%20Kolhan%20(south)%20regions.%20The%20BJP%20could%20manage%20to%20win%20just%20two%20ST%20seats%20in%202019%2C%20down%20from%2011%20in%202014.%20This%20poor%20show%20is%20often%20cited%20as%20one%20of%20the%20main%20reasons%20for%20its%20loss%20in%202019.%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20swept%20these%20two%20regions%20in%202019%2C%20winning%20all%20the%2016%20seats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChampai%20himself%20hails%20from%20the%20Kolhan%20region%2C%20which%20includes%20East%20and%20West%20Singhbhum%20and%20Saraikela%20districts%2C%20and%20houses%20the%20industrial%20town%20of%20Jamshedpur.%20While%20the%20BJP%20had%20won%20five%20of%20the%2014%20seats%20here%20in%202014%2C%20in%20the%20next%20assembly%20election%2C%20it%20drew%20a%20blank.%20The%20party%20now%20hopes%20Champai%20Soren's%20name%20will%20help%20it%20not%20only%20reverse%20its%20fortunes%20in%20the%20region%20but%20also%20bag%20a%20section%20of%20ST%20votes%20in%20the%20state%20overall%2C%20while%20it%20tries%20to%20consolidate%20OBC%2C%20upper%20caste%20and%20SC%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Close%20Contest%20In%20Jharkhand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20four%20states%20that%20will%20see%20elections%20to%20their%20assemblies%20this%20year%20-%20the%20other%20three%20being%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%2C%20Maharashtra%20and%20Haryana%20-%20Jharkhand%20is%20the%20only%20one%20where%20the%20BJP%20is%20not%20in%20power.%20As%20of%20now%2C%20the%20battle%20in%20the%20state%20is%20shaping%20up%20to%20be%20a%20close%2C%20seat-by-seat%20contest.%20A%20bulk%20of%20the%20BJP's%20weak%20seats%20are%20in%20Santhal%20Pargana%20and%20Kolhan%20divisions%2C%20where%20Champai%20can%20help.%20In%20the%20latter%2C%20the%20huge%20Kurmi%20population%20has%20turned%20against%20the%20JMM%20as%20their%20demand%20for%20being%20included%20in%20the%20ST%20category%20hasn't%20been%20met.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20entrant%20Jairam%20Mahato's%20Jharkhandi%20Bhasha%20Khatian%20Sangharsh%20Samiti%20(JBKSS)%20could%20play%20spoilsport%20here.%20In%20this%20year's%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20its%20entry%20split%20the%20opposition%20votes%2C%20which%20ultimately%20helped%20the%20BJP.%20The%20party%20bagged%20over%201.25%20lakh%20votes%20in%20three%20seats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Sarna%20Code%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere's%20another%20social%20factor.%20In%20recent%20years%2C%20many%20tribals%20have%20converted%20to%20Christianity%2C%20which%20has%20caused%20social%20friction.%20Tribal%20Christians%20dominate%20politics%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20JMM.%20The%20BJP%20has%20been%20exploiting%20these%20tensions%2C%20with%20most%20ST%20voters%20backing%20it%20being%20'Sarna'%20tribals%2C%20who%20follow%20nature%20worship.%20Even%20so%2C%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20got%20some%20support%20from%20them%20as%20it%20promised%20to%20fulfil%20a%20long-time%20demand%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20reluctant%20to%20consider%3A%20the%20implementation%20of%20a%20'Sarna%20Code'%2C%20which%20proposes%20a%20separate%20religious%20code%20for%20tribals%20who%20follow%20the%20Sarna%20religion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20Champai%20Soren%20had%20promised%20to%20fulfil%20this%20demand%20and%20even%20accused%20the%20Centre%20of%20dragging%20its%20feet%20on%20it.%20It%20will%20be%20interesting%20to%20see%20how%20he%20now%20manages%20to%20balance%20this.%20Undoubtedly%2C%20the%20JMM%20will%20try%20to%20play%20up%20this%20'doublespeak'%20to%20attack%20Soren.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBattle%20Lines%20Drawn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JMM%20hopes%20to%20consolidate%20its%20SC-ST-Muslim%20vote%20base%2C%20which%20accounts%20for%2050%25%20of%20the%20state's%20population.%20It%20also%20hopes%20that%20Mahato's%20party%20will%20split%20the%20Kurmi%20vote%2C%20damaging%20the%20prospects%20of%20the%20All%20Jharkhand%20Students%20Union%20(AJSU).%20It%20is%20also%20counting%20on%20the%20Congress%20to%20tap%20some%20urban%20voters%20after%20its%20improved%20national%20performance%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20working%20on%20a%20state-level%20narrative%20to%20highlight%20the%20failures%20of%20the%20Hemant%20Soren%20government%20and%20its%20non-fulfilment%20of%20promises%20like%20unemployment%20allowance%20to%20youth%2C%20stove%20expense%20allowance%20to%20women%2C%20etc.%20It's%20also%20hoping%20to%20attract%20young%20voters%20by%20highlighting%20the%20state's%20jobs%20problem%20and%20its%20own%20promises%20in%20the%20recent%20Union%20Budget.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20keen%20battle%20is%20on%20the%20cards.%20Champai's%20entry%20definitely%20strengthens%20the%20BJP%2C%20but%20it%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20whether%20he%20can%20ultimately%20deliver%20a%20win.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725015720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fo52rdhug_champai_625x300_30_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fnow-that-champai-soren-has-finally-joined-bjp-can-he-help-it-win-6452519%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20hopes%20that%20Champai%20Soren's%20name%20will%20help%20it%20not%20only%20reverse%20its%20fortunes%20in%20the%20region%20but%20also%20bag%20a%20section%20of%20ST%20votes%20in%20the%20state%20overall.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fnow-that-champai-soren-has-finally-joined-bjp-can-he-help-it-win-6452519%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Enough%20Proof%20To%20Charge%20Jagdish%20Tytler%20In%201984%20Anti-Sikh%20Riots%20Case%3A%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Delhi%20court%20on%20Friday%20directed%20framing%20of%20charges%2C%20including%20murder%20and%20provocation%20with%20intent%20to%20cause%20riot%2C%20against%20Congress%20leader%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fjagdish-tytler%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJagdish%20Tytler%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20case%20related%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20Thakur%20Singh%2C%20Badal%20Singh%2C%20and%20Gurcharan%20Singh%2C%20outside%20the%20Pul%20Bangash%20gurdwara%20in%20the%20city%2C%20during%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2F1984-anti-sikh-riots%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanti-Sikh%20riots%20of%201984%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20case%20had%20been%20registered%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormal%20charges%20-%C2%A0%20unlawful%20assembly%2C%20rioting%2C%20disobedience%20to%20order%2C%20defiling%20a%20place%20of%20worship%2C%20abetment)%2C%20mischief%20by%20fire%2C%20and%20theft%2C%20apart%20from%20murder%20and%20intent%20to%20cause%20a%20riot%20-%C2%A0will%20be%20framed%20on%20September%2013%2C%20when%20Tytler%20will%20be%20be%20present%20to%20enter%20a%20plea%20-%20either%20'guilty'%20or%20'not%20guilty'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%2C%20in%20a%20chargesheet%20filed%20in%20May%20last%20year%2C%20had%20accused%20Tytler%2C%20a%20former%20Union%20Minister%2C%20of%20%26quot%3Binciting%2C%20instigating%20and%20provoking%20the%20mob%26quot%3B%20assembled%20near%20the%20gurdwara%20in%20November%201984.%20In%20concluding%20arguments%20in%20January%2C%20the%20federal%20agency%20presented%20eyewitnesses'%20statements%20and%20told%20the%20court%20there%20is%20sufficient%20evidence%20to%20frame%20charges%20against%20the%20Congress%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTytler%20provoked%20the%20mob%20to%20kill%20Sikhs%20which%20resulted%20in%20Gurudwara%20Pul%20Bangash%20being%20set%20on%20fire%20by%20the%20mob%20and%20killing%20of%20three%20persons%20belonging%20to%20Sikh%20community...%26quot%3B%20the%20CBI%20told%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcbi-sa