-desk-coworkers-didnt-notice-body-for-4-days-6451469%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Arizona%20Wells%20Fargo%20employee%20was%20found%20dead%20at%20her%20desk%20four%20days%20after%20clocking%20into%20work.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwells-fargo-employee-dies-at-desk-coworkers-didnt-notice-body-for-4-days-6451469%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Never%20Before%20Has%20Defence%20Been%20So%20Important%20For%20India-US%20Ties%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fmhjbm4m8_india-us_625x300_30_August_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US-India%20defence%20relationship%20is%20rapidly%20expanding%2C%20adapting%20to%20evolving%20regional%20and%20global%20security%20demands.%20This%20includes%20safeguarding%20supply%20chains%2C%20advancing%20critical%20and%20emerging%20technologies%2C%20and%20enhancing%20cooperation%20in%20cyber%2C%20space%2C%20and%20new%20dimensions%20of%20battlespace%20dominance.%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh's%20visit%20to%20the%20US%20from%20August%2023-26%20highlighted%20these%20shifts%2C%20aiming%20to%20bridge%20bilateral%20gaps%20in%20these%20critical%20areas.%20The%20visit%20underscored%20a%20clear%20trend%3A%20while%20major%20defence%20deals%20continue%20to%20strengthen%20traditional%20security%20ties%2C%20both%20nations%20are%20increasingly%20emphasising%20emerging%20strategic%20elements%20to%20integrate%20the%20security%20partnership%20with%20a%20purposive%20intent%20towards%20making%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region%20free%20and%20open.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIssues%20central%20to%20joint%20India-US%20interests%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20and%20the%20security%20of%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20are%20being%20prioritised.%20India's%20increasing%20role%20in%20shaping%20regional%20security%20by%20ensuring%20freedom%20of%20navigation%2C%20now%20especially%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Combined%20Maritime%20Force%20(CMF)%2C%20was%20acknowledged.%20With%20India%20assuming%20leadership%20in%20the%20Combined%20Task%20Force%20150%20in%202025%2C%20stakes%20for%20an%20expanded%20regional%20security%20role%20have%20increased%20for%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Indo-Pacific%20Arena%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20remains%20central%20to%20regional%20and%20global%20security%2C%20enhancing%20partnership%20in%20this%20region%20is%20key%20to%20shaping%20a%20regionally%20favourable%20security%20architecture.%20Towards%20this%2C%20the%20visit%20provided%20an%20opportunity%20for%20steps%20in%20increasing%20supply%20chain%20security%20as%20well%20as%20enhancing%20maritime%20security%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean.%20Among%20the%20highlights%20was%20a%20new%20agreement%20to%20expand%20and%20strengthen%20operational%20coordination%20between%20India%20and%20the%20US%20by%20placing%20Indian%20liaison%20officers%20at%20US%20commands.%20The%20agreement%20is%20a%20step%20up%20for%20regional%20security%20coordination%20and%20domain%20awareness%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20for%20India%2C%20complementing%20an%20earlier%20initiative%20to%20host%20US%20officers%20at%20the%20Information%20Fusion%20Centre%20(IFC-IOR)%20in%20India.%20It%20also%20overcomes%20the%20capacity%20limitations%20of%20India%2C%20indeed%20any%20country%2C%20to%20solely%20monitor%20the%20vast%20expanse%20of%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20on%20a%20real-time%20basis.%20Beyond%20the%20Indo-Pacific%2C%20placing%20Indian%20liaison%20officers%20at%20the%20other%2010%20Combatant%20Commands%20could%20usher%20new%20vistas%20in%20information%20sharing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20visit%20were%20steps%20to%20strengthen%20the%20Major%20Defence%20Partnership%20(MDP)%20and%20provide%20fresh%20momentum%20to%20joint%20production%2C%20including%20the%20reigniting%20of%20the%20Defense%20Trade%20and%20Technology%20Initiative%20(DTTI).%20Under%20the%20US-India%20Roadmap%20for%20Defense%20Industrial%20Cooperation%2C%20an%20agreement%20to%20jointly%20produce%20jet%20engines%2C%20unmanned%20platforms%2C%20munitions%2C%20and%20ground%20mobility%20systems%20was%20signed.%20Leading%20up%20to%20the%20third%20summit%20of%20the%20India-U.S.%20Defense%20Acceleration%20Ecosystem%20(INDUS-X)%20to%20be%20held%20in%20September%20in%20the%20US%2C%20discussions%20to%20expand%20cooperation%20in%20the%20areas%20of%20undersea%20and%20space-related%20collaborations%20were%20timely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20SOSA%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20significant%20outcomes%20of%20the%20visit%20was%20the%20signing%20of%20the%20Security%20of%20Supply%20Arrangement%20(SOSA)%2C%20which%20makes%20India%20the%2018th%20country%20to%20enter%20into%20this%20agreement%20with%20the%20US.%20It%20reflects%20a%20shared%20long-term%20vision%20to%20seamlessly%20integrate%20the%20defence%20industrial%20ecosystems%20of%20both%20nations%20while%20safeguarding%20supply%20chains%20from%20future%20disruptions.%20SOSA%20complements%20the%20Major%20Defense%20Partnership%20(MDP)%20and%20the%20Defense%20Technology%20and%20Trade%20Initiative%20(DTTI).%20Notably%2C%20the%20visit%20aimed%20to%20reinvigorate%20the%20DTTI%2C%20a%20co-production%20initiative%20launched%20with%20high%20expectations%2C%20but%20that%20had%20lost%20momentum.%20The%20Under%20Secretary%20of%20Defense%20for%20Acquisition%20and%20Sustainment%20will%20host%20a%20DTTI%20meeting%20in%20the%20coming%20months%2C%20bringing%20together%20government%20and%20private%20stakeholders%20from%20both%20countries'%20defence%20industries.%20The%20DTTI's%20primary%20goal%20is%20to%20integrate%20the%20defence%20industrial%20bases%20of%20the%20US%20and%20India%2C%20promoting%20bilateral%20co-development%2C%20co-production%2C%20and%20co-sustainment%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESOSA%20strengthens%20the%20partnership%20by%20establishing%20guardrails%20for%20supply%20chains%20between%20the%20two%20countries'%20defence%20industries%2C%20which%20are%20poised%20to%20grow%20with%20new%20co-production%20and%20co-development%20opportunities.%20Guided%20by%20the%20US%20Defense%20Priorities%20and%20Allocations%20System%20(DPAS)%2C%20the%20arrangement%20provides%20structural%20and%20institutional%20assurances%20for%20defense%20supplies.%20India%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20develop%20a%20common%20code%20of%20conduct%20for%20government%20and%20industry%20stakeholders%2C%20prioritizing%20critical%20supplies%20to%20the%20US%20on%20a%20voluntary%20basis.%20With%20SOSA%20in%20place%2C%20working%20groups%20will%20have%20the%20framework%20to%20communicate%20more%20frequently%20and%20take%20proactive%20steps%20to%20ensure%20supply%20chain%20stability%20in%20both%20peacetime%20and%20crisis%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDiaspora%20As%20A%20'Living%20Bridge'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh's%20reference%20to%20the%20Indian%20diaspora%20in%20the%20US%20as%20a%20'living%20bridge'%20now%20resonates%20within%20the%20context%20of%20the%20growing%20India-US%20defence%20relationship.%20This%20June%20marked%20the%20first%20anniversary%20of%20the%20US-India%20INDUS-X%20Initiative%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20build%20a%20defence%20innovation%20bridge%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20under%20the%20Initiative%20on%20Critical%20and%20Emerging%20Technology%20(iCET).%20By%20connecting%20researchers%2C%20investors%2C%20and%20defence%20tech%20companies%20from%20both%20nations%2C%20INDUS-X%20outlines%20a%20strategy%20to%20harness%20private%20capital%20for%20defence%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20the%20US%20are%20swiftly%20adapting%20to%20the%20evolving%20global%20security%20landscape%2C%20responding%20to%20new%20threat%20perceptions%20with%20increased%20innovation%20and%20cooperation%20in%20advanced%20domains.%20The%20second%20US-India%20Advanced%20Domains%20Defense%20Dialogue%20(AD3)%20held%20this%20year%20underscored%20the%20importance%20of%20coordination%20in%20emerging%20defence%20areas%2C%20including%20space%2C%20cyber%2C%20and%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20while%20identifying%20critical%20sub-sectors%20for%20potential%20industrial%20collaboration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Next%20Goals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Defence%20Minister%20also%20visited%20the%20Naval%20Surface%20Warfare%20Center%20in%20Memphis%2C%20accompanied%20by%20a%20delegation%20from%20the%20Defence%20Research%20and%20Development%20Organisation%20(DRDO)%2C%20signalling%20a%20potential%20pathway%20for%20co-learning%20and%20development.%20In%20a%20boost%20to%20India's%20Anti-Submarine%20Warfare%20(ASW)%20capabilities%2C%20India%20secured%20the%20purchase%20of%20sonobuoys%20from%20the%20US%20in%20the%20lead-up%20to%20the%20visit.%20The%20acquisition%20and%20co-production%20of%20General%20Atomics'%20MQ-9B%20remotely%20piloted%20aircraft%20systems%20and%20the%20joint%20production%20of%20GE%20F414%20jet%20engines%20in%20India%20are%20the%20next%20major%20goals%20for%20both%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajnath%20Singh's%20visit%20managed%20to%20underline%20once%20again%20that%20defence%20is%20the%20main%20driver%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20shaping%20the%20trajectory%20of%20US-India%20bilateral%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Harsh%20V%20Pant%20is%20Vice%20President%20for%20Studies%20at%20ORF%20and%20Professor%20at%20King's%20College%20London.%20Vivek%20Mishra%20is%20Fellow%2C%20Americas%2C%20at%20ORF.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20authors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725009720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fkaljk808_india-u