tion%2C%20it%20was%20a%20game-changer%20for%20him.%20Since%20then%2C%20he%20has%20never%20looked%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20began%20training%20under%20Gaurav%20Khanna%2C%20the%20head%20coach%20of%20the%20Indian%20para-badminton%20team%20and%20a%20Dronacharya%20awardee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20began%20competing%20internationally%2C%20earning%20a%20bronze%20medal%20at%20the%202018%20Asian%20Para%20Games%20and%20the%20World%20Para%20Badminton%20Championships%20in%202019.%20His%20defining%20moment%20came%20with%20winning%20the%20gold%20medal%20in%20the%20men%E2%80%99s%20singles%20SH6%20category%20at%20the%20Tokyo%202020%20Paralympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20handling%20nerves%20at%20such%20big-stakes%20competitions%2C%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3ESportstar%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20being%20calm.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20times%20it%20happens%20that%20when%20you%20are%20playing%20such%20a%20big%20tournament%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20how%20you%20can%20control%20yourself%2C%20your%20emotions%3B%20that%20becomes%20more%20important.%20When%20you%20come%20into%20such%20a%20big%20tournament%2C%20you%20have%20to%20stay%20a%20little%20calm%20and%20play%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20country%20celebrated%20his%20triumph%2C%20he%20faced%20a%20major%20blow%20when%20his%20mother%20passed%20away%20six%20months%20after%20his%20victory.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20too%20many%20hurdles%20after%20her%20passing%20away.%20She%20was%20my%20everything.%20But%20then%20my%20mental%20situation%20worsened%20after%20her%20death.%20I%20sunk%20into%20darkness%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20friends%20and%20badminton%20helped%20pull%20him%20away%20from%20the%20dark%20place.%20He%20decided%20to%20do%20his%20best%20and%20started%20working%20on%20defending%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F337854%2Fsheetal-devi-arjuna-awar