%20to%20be%20part%20of%20his%20cause.%20I%20also%20dedicate%202-3%20days%20in%20a%20week%20to%20teach%20students%20when%20Amit%20sir%20is%20on%20duty.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20emphasises%20the%20importance%20of%20holistic%20development%20and%20encourages%20children%20to%20explore%20various%20paths%20to%20success.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20some%20children%20secure%20government%20jobs%2C%20some%20choose%20to%20return%20to%20their%20villages%20to%20do%20farming%20after%20unsuccessful%20attempts.%20The%20aim%20is%20to%20make%20them%20self-reliant%20and%20prevent%20them%20from%20engaging%20in%20criminal%20activities%20in%20greed%20of%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20his%20perseverance%20and%20selfless%20dedication%2C%20Amit%20continues%20to%20be%20an%20inspiration%20for%20hundreds%20of%20underprivileged%20children.%20On%20his%20commitment%20to%20providing%20a%20better%20future%20for%20the%20next%20generation%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20received%20multiple%20awards%20for%20this%20work.%20But%20I%20am%20not%20doing%20this%20work%20for%20a%20%3Cem%3Epuraskar%20%3C%2Fem%3E(award)%20but%20for%20%3Cem%3Epurushartha%20%3C%2Fem%3E(purpose%20of%20human%20being).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCurrently%2C%20I%20am%20able%20to%20take%20in%20only%2030%20children%20every%20year%20due%20to%20financial%20constraints%20but%20there%20are%20so%20many%20children%20who%20require%20the%20support.%20I%20wish%20that%20more%20people%20extend%20their%20support%20for%20the%20future%20of%20these%20children.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20seek%20financial%20support%20but%20people%20can%20donate%20stationery%2C%20notebooks%2C%20old%20books%2C%20and%20dry%20ration%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photo%3A%20Amit%20Lathia.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724919280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Famit-lathia-1-1724916746.jpg%22