5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20started%20by%20cooking%20authentic%20Kathiyawadi%20dishes%20using%20fresh%20and%20local%20ingredients%20from%20the%20farm.%20What%20attracts%20viewers%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20takes%20us%20through%20the%20process%20of%20sourcing%20the%20ingredients%20and%20cooks%20them%20on%20the%20farm%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20channel%20%E2%80%98Crazy%20For%20Indian%20Food%E2%80%99%20has%20over%205.9%20lakh%20subscribers%2C%20with%20the%20most%20popular%20video%20having%20a%20whopping%209.1%20million%20views!%20Besides%20cooking%20food%2C%20he%20also%20reviews%20popular%20street%20food%20joints%20and%20restaurants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20with%20one%20channel%20in%202013%2C%20he%20has%20expanded%20to%20running%20a%20network%20called%20Foodon%20TV%2C%20which%20runs%20six%20channels%20and%20four%20websites%20in%20six%20languages.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20rose%20to%20fame%2C%20he%20also%20battled%20with%20personal%20problems%20as%20he%20got%20divorced.%20However%2C%20not%20one%20to%20lose%20hope%2C%20he%20focused%20on%20his%20career%20and%20found%20love%20again%20in%202021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20authentic%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F327829%2Flilyma-khan-head-chef-at-dear-donna-delhi-shares-struggle-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKathiyawadi%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20fans%20in%20the%20Ambanis%20too%2C%20who%20invited%20him%20to%20cook%20at%20their%20New%20Year%E2%80%99s%20dinner%2C%20catapulting%20him%20to%20fame!%20He%20also%20cooked%20for%20Anant%20Ambani%20and%20Radhika%20Merchant%E2%80%99s%20pre-wedding%20ceremony%20in%20Vantara%20and%20wedding%20in%20Mumbai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dishes%20included%20Jamnagari%20Sev%2C%20Mamra%20Lili%20Chutney%2C%20Desi%20Sev%20Tamera%20Shaak%2C%20and%20Bajra%20Rotla%20and%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNever%20give%20up%2C%20dream%20big%2C%20work%20on%20it%2C%20and%20it%20will