0opportunity%20to%20bring%20their%20solution%20to%20life%20during%20a%20STEM%20competition%20in%202022.%20They%20asked%20themselves%3A%20%E2%80%9CCould%20we%20create%20a%20preventative%20tool%20that%20would%20anticipate%20the%20risk%20of%20falls%20and%20alert%20caregivers%20in%20time%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20course%20of%20two%20years%2C%20the%2018-year-olds%20dedicated%20themselves%20to%20developing%20Walkfit%20%E2%80%94%20a%20system%20that%20attaches%20to%20a%20walking%20stick%20to%20assist%20with%20gait%20analysis%20and%20diagnose%20lower%20limb%20orthopaedic%20disorders.%20The%20teenagers%20utilised%20robotics%2C%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%2C%20and%20machine%20learning%20(ML)%20skills%20they%20honed%20at%20Omotec%20(On%20My%20Own%20Technology).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahi%20and%20Hriday%20have%20won%20many%20accolades%2C%20emerging%20as%20runner-ups%20at%20the%20IIT%20Bombay%20Techfest%20and%20securing%20a%20provisional%20patent%20for%20their%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20Walkfit%20can%20help%20elders%20with%20mobility%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20Lego%20to%20real%20robots%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahi%20and%20Hriday%E2%80%99s%20interest%20in%20robotics%20received%20a%20fillip%20when%20their%20school%2C%20Podar%20International%2C%20started%20a%20robotics%20lab%20in%202019.%20Then%20just%2012%2C%20the%20duo%20participated%20in%20a%20competition%2C%20that%20cemented%20their%20passion%20for%20the%20subject.%20To%20further%20their%20interest%2C%20they%20joined%20Omotec%20and%20did%20a%20course%20in%20Python%2C%20a%20programming%20language.%20Over%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20done%20various%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F334179%2Fteenage-changemakers-of-india-children-founders-of-startups-ngos-inspiring%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecourses%20in%20robotics%