20six!)%20to%20go.%20Old%20school%20%E2%80%94%20done%20right!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Veronica%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20ever-changing%20dynamics%20of%20cuisines%20across%20the%20globe%2C%20the%20popularity%20of%20finger%20food%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20dimmed%20a%20bit.%20And%20one%20spot%20in%20the%20posh%20Bandra%20suburb%20of%20Mumbai%2C%20Veronica%E2%80%99s%20is%20giving%20this%20range%20of%20snacks%20their%20dues%20through%20their%20sausage%20rolls%2C%20shrimp%20popcorn%2C%20mushroom%20puffs%2C%20and%20croissants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FWbWN5LVBsPo%3Fsi%3Dckyo81k8drX_z5ql%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistory%20aficionados%20will%20be%20delighted%20to%20know%20that%20Veronica%E2%80%99s%20is%20located%20in%20an%20erstwhile%20bakery%2C%20which%20marked%20a%20significant%20spot%20in%20the%20city%20in%20the%20early%2070s.%20In%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Cem%3EArchitectural%20Digest%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Sameer%20Seth%2C%20co-founder%20of%20Hunger%20Inc%20recounted%20an%20anecdote%20of%20how%20this%20St%20Jude%20Bakery%20was%20the%20first%20choice%20for%20families%2C%20who%20did%20not%20possess%20an%20oven%2C%20to%20send%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F227895%2Findia-best-bakeries-iconic-kayani-pune-kolkata-nahoum-glenary-wengers-delhi-ang136%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edough%20and%20cakes%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20when%20they%20needed%20to%20be%20baked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Kyani%20%26amp%3B%20Co%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZoroastrian%20migration%20and%20its%20attendant%20cuisine%20have%20been%20grafting%20itself%20into%20Indian%20gastronomy%20since%20the%2010